{"tid":1895672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020立會選舉] 對家做咁多嘢準備立會，我地再淨係咩都唔做期望支爆實輸","createTime":"2020-02-24T16:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T17:09:19.000Z","uid":286041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3970235de71c1a8a4c4ae00361184e1a155d3d","tid":1895672,"uid":286041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"對家做咁多嘢又派口罩又盛，加上藍屍輸咗上次區會埸選舉，肯定出盡全力去動員<br />\n<br />\n我哋再咩都唔做齋坐睇支爆，得閒笑吓支拿唱吓歌仔肯定輸硬！！！<br />\n<br />\n希望各位開始做準備，特別係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">功能界別啲選民登記</span>，沈旭輝搵到多一個界別門檻極低，要5月前搞掂先有資格<br />\n<br />\n1. 無限登記選民嘅功能界別(進出口界)：<br />\n成本只係千幾蚊，有間運作咗一年嘅公司(任何類型嘅工司都得)，就可以申請個烈酒進口牌，即時做選民(公司票)<br />\n而家呢個界別得千幾個選民，肯叫多啲中小企做一定可以拎埋呢個界別<br />\n*登記好似5月頭截止<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機會拎到一半議席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%A5%AA%E5%8D%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%8B%BC%E5%9C%96-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E5%92%81%E5%81%9A/?fbclid=IwAR1k3ArXFACoGQyluZG5fO1TVhFvQJQumobY3b_L5Kmg6dWwQj3ZUpJq6kw#.Xkgl8a18Dzs.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%258D%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%258B%25BC%25E5%259C%2596-%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%258F%25AA%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%2581%259A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1k3ArXFACoGQyluZG5fO1TVhFvQJQumobY3b_L5Kmg6dWwQj3ZUpJq6kw%23.Xkgl8a18Dzs.facebook&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=50fccd4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%258D%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%258B%25BC%25E5%259C%2596-%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%258F%25AA%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%2581%259A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1k3ArXFACoGQyluZG5fO1TVhFvQJQumobY3b_L5Kmg6dWwQj3ZUpJq6kw%23.Xkgl8a18Dzs.facebook&h=bcde430c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%A5%AA%E5%8D%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%8B%BC%E5%9C%96-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E5%92%81%E5%81%9A/?fbclid=IwAR1k3ArXFACoGQyluZG5fO1TVhFvQJQumobY3b_L5Kmg6dWwQj3ZUpJq6kw#.Xkgl8a18Dzs.facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 另外，關於選舉以及達到五大訴求可行路線嘅分析：<br />\n<br />\n全文：全文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3064023730298423/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F3064023730298423%2F&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=90d35396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3064023730298423/</a><br />\n<br />\n#sorry for 1999，只係希望大家唔好坐係度等支爆啫<br />\n#希望至少開始翻立會嘅準備，係能力範圍做到嘅嘢盡早做<br />\n# 尊重翻傳媒人，入原link睇"},{"pid":"929c4996a47b32b14536c7a71ec5edc851832c10","tid":1895672,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"b17a06436819b6b2ec5b7240dc29b567494555f0","tid":1895672,"uid":72361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"24a90595e23fb75463730183ac146513ebeae359","tid":1895672,"uid":319616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啱 依家準備立法會選舉差唔多</span></span>"},{"pid":"422711df622a8fcbe21f5de42efe4578e91adc1f","tid":1895672,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"蕭生都講到口臭 係時候要準備喇"}]}